{"tid":1849009,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隱瞞參與千人計劃 哈佛大學化學系主任被捕","createTime":"2020-01-28T19:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T23:03:06.000Z","uid":141151,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"770ebf8dc82680d226352449f0c4829a60c281fc","tid":1849009,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T19:49:07.000Z","msg":"隱瞞參與千人計劃 哈佛大學化學系主任被捕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/1/28/n11828117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F1%2F28%2Fn11828117.htm&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JnPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=4ca72e43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/1/28/n11828117.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2020年01月29日訊】哈佛大學化學系主任週二（1月28日）被美國司法部刑事指控，美方指控他參與中共「千人計劃」、卻沒有對美國國防部以及國立衛生研究院（NIH）說實話。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報導說，這是美國政府針對北京在美國大學進行「野心勃勃」招募努力，進行的反制升級舉措。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根據刑事指控書，哈佛大學化學系教授查爾斯&middot;利伯（Charles Lieber）涉嫌對國防部和國立衛生研究院（National Institutes of Health）撒謊，他參與了中國（中共）的「千人計劃」，但沒有向美國當局透露他獲得中國（中共）政府資助。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n利伯是納米電子領域的傑出人才，從武漢理工大學哈佛大學納米聯合實驗室獲得5萬美元的月薪、15.8萬美元的生活費以及174萬研究經費。<br />\n<br />\n司法部週二在波士頓共指控了三名為中國工作的科學家。利伯於週二被捕，因為他既不是中國人、也不是中國血統；此外， 作為哈佛大學的系主任，他的業內聲望遠超之前被捕或起訴的美國科學家。<br />\n<br />\n美國官員正在通過訪問科學家調查數百起涉嫌盜竊知識產權的案件，其中幾乎所有案件都是中國公民或華裔。 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一些人被指控在美國政府資助的基礎上在中國獲得專利，其他人則被指控在中國建立祕密複製美國研究成果的實驗室。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國聯邦調查局（FBI）在週二發出的新聞稿中說，千人計劃獎勵個人竊取專有信息以及違反出口管制。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n美國當局已經對中共政府實施的海外人才招募計劃提出警告，官員們說，這種人才計劃在製造利益衝突，並為海外科研人員將美國的知識產權帶回中國提供了一種激勵。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部最近幾個月針對「千人計劃」起訴了數人，指控這些美國大學和實驗室的研究人員沒有披露他們從這類中共官方贊助的計劃中獲得資金，或者是指控他們試圖竊取信息帶到中國。#<br />\n<br />\nHarvard professor Charles Lieber charged with hiding China ties<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.boston.com/news/crime/2020/01/28/harvard-professor-charles-lieber-charged-with-hiding-china-ties\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boston.com%2Fnews%2Fcrime%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2Fharvard-professor-charles-lieber-charged-with-hiding-china-ties&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JnPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=ffab9e9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.boston.com/news/crime/2020/01/28/harvard-professor-charles-lieber-charged-with-hiding-china-ties</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHarvard University Professor and Two Chinese Nationals Charged in Three Separate China Related Cases<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.justice.gov/usao-ma/pr/harvard-university-professor-and-two-chinese-nationals-charged-three-separate-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-ma%2Fpr%2Fharvard-university-professor-and-two-chinese-nationals-charged-three-separate-china&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JnPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=77c2d896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.justice.gov/usao-ma/pr/harvard-university-professor-and-two-chinese-nationals-charged-three-separate-china</a>"},{"pid":"1a61d0ec93790e21b8d7e926b214edc332915fc2","tid":1849009,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T19:51:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e40b94ec636987c8ec8a9e034fb85e622774a15f","tid":1849009,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T19:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f14189e9d50db70ff7f389e525496859b756985","tid":1849009,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T19:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8a56b703c76ba6905ec3af75db6723c059f61c","tid":1849009,"uid":252920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T19:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821c602d5219ca779aa72fb8de1a2cda67341ffd","tid":1849009,"uid":258770,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"repl